<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Jak zostać drillowcem</title>
    <style>
        @font-face {
            font-family: 'JudasCaps';
            src: url('judasc__.ttf');
        }
        
        
        *{
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        body{
            background-color: #3b3b8f;
            display: flex;
            height: 100vh;
            color: white;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        nav{
            width: 250px;
            background-color: #5b5ba8;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .btn{
            background-color: #4a4a9b;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 15px 10px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .btn-small{
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            margin-top: auto;
            background: none;
            text-align: left;
            padding: 5px;
        }

        main{
            flex-grow: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h2{
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        .logo-text{
            font-size: 9rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: #8fbdfa;
            line-height: 0.8;
            font-family: 'JudasCaps', serif;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .secret-text{
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #8fbdfa;
            opacity: 0.6;
            transform: scaleY(-1);
            margin-top: 20px;
            letter-spacing: 12px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <button class="btn">co kupić?</button>
        <button class="btn">czego nie robić?</button>
        <button class="btn">jak sie zachowywać?</button>
        <button class="btn ">jak bardzo ociekasz?</button>
    </nav>
    
    <main>
        <h2>JAK ZOSTAĆ DRILLOWCEM</h2>
        <div class="logo-text">TRAPSTAR</div>
        <div class="secret-text">IT'S A SECRET</div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
